<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:91.34px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">8 Most Expensive Headphones on the Market</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:113.78px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">You Won’t Regret Purchasing Them!</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:171.26px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Are you wondering why we are talking about the most expensive headphones on the market</span></div>
