<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:214.94px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">types. You can get a good pair of headphones for less than $50 or purchase high-end</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:229.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">headphones to make the most of premium features, such as excellent comfort, plush padding,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:244.13px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">smart technology and so on. The choice is completely yours. However, since we have already</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:258.65px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">covered the best budget headphones in one of our guides, we decided to shed some light on</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:273.17px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">the most expensive headphones on the market this time around.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:302.21px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">To get you the list of the best and most expensive headphones, we shortlisted 20 high-end</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:316.85px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">headphones and tested them through and through to find the 8 most expensive headphones</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:331.37px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">that are trending. These extravagant headphones can be a perfect pick for those who are not on</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:345.89px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">a shoestring budget. Read further to know more.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:378.53px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">How to Find the Most Expensive Headphones</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:417.31px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Apart from a high price (which is already your main purchase criteria), ensure you also consider</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:431.83px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">the following factors while looking for high-end headphones:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:472.99px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1. </span><span class="cls_006"> Purpose -</span><span class="cls_002"> After price, the second most important factor you should consider is the</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:487.63px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">reason for purchasing the headphones. Are you looking for the most expensive</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:502.15px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">headphones for mixing? Do you need expensive headphones to complete your gaming</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:516.67px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">setup? Or do you simply want to buy expensive headphones for an incredible listening</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:531.19px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">experience? Ensure you know why exactly you want to buy expensive headphones to</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:545.71px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">make an informed purchase.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:560.47px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">2. </span><span class="cls_006"> Comfort and fit -</span><span class="cls_002"> Most of the expensive headphones (and even earphones) are heavy</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:575.02px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">duty. Since their price is high, they comprise all premium-quality elements to make them</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:589.54px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">sturdy and durable. Therefore, before purchasing the headphones, ensure they are</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:604.06px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">comfortable. Also, it would be a good idea to purchase headphones with adjustable</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:618.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">headbands and rotating ear cups.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:656.26px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Sound quality is also one of the most critical factors you should look at and it goes without</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:670.78px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">saying. However, we are not talking about it in detail as we strongly believe that all expensive</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:685.30px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">headphones deliver great sound quality. You’ll see that when you start reading the product</span></div>
