<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:71.28px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Out of all the gaming headphones we tested, we found the ASUS gaming headset to be the</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:85.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">most expensive and best performing gaming headset. The moment you look at the headset, you</span></div>
