<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:187.70px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">excellent audio quality.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:216.74px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Secondly, the headset comes with a plug-and-play USB control box that functions like a USB</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:231.26px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">sound card, and provides noise cancelation and multiple audio profiles. It also functions as a</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:245.93px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">headphone amplifier</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:274.97px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Thirdly, the ASUS ROG Centurion Gaming Headset also justifies its high-end price by providing</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:289.49px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">the utmost comfort during unending gaming sessions. The ear cups are covered with soft and</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:304.13px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">premium-end leather ear cushions. We did not experience any ear fatigue whatsoever.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:333.17px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Lastly, the wired gaming headset comprises a high-quality microphone that is highly sensitive to</span></div>
