<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:288.41px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">quality of calls.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:317.45px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Secondly, the headphones come with built-in voice assistance powered by the Amazon Alexa.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:331.97px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">However, whether you are communicating with Alexa or listening to your favorite music, you can</span></div>
