<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:361.13px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1000XM4 Headphones died while we were at the beach; however, a quick 15-minute charge</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:375.65px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">provided almost 6 hours of battery life.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:404.81px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Lastly, the headphones are comfortable and sturdy. The music automatically pauses when you</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:419.35px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">remove the headphones and starts playing when you wear them again. Overall, the Sony WH-</span></div>
